My shinies

Here is a list of my shinies from every Pokémon game that has shinies.

I currently have over 250 shinies which may not be visible as this page is a work in progress. I can only fit the sprite, species name, and nickname in the table but if you want to see more info about each shiny—including how I got it and what game it came from—you can check out the JSON file where all the data lives.

Note: if names are separated by a slash, it means I have more than one.

Images courtesy of The Spriters Resource
